Package branch

Class Branch

java.lang.Object
branch.Branch
public class Branch extends Object
  • Class representing branch of the Fast-Food chain
  • The branch is of entity stereotype and composes of other classes and actors like staff and customer
  • This class serves more as a all-encompompassing tool to host operations and users within a fast-food branch
    • Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    FDAB 2

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes
      Modifier and Type
      Class
      Description
      static enum 
      Branch.OperationStatus
      Class object representing if the branch is closed or open A branch being closed is to be differentiated from a branch being "shut down" Certain attributes like all the branch's staff and menu remain when the branch is closed.Preventing the need to re-initialize upon opening branch at opening hours
